{"tid":469981,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拖定唔拖？","createTime":"2017-11-16T00:36:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-21T11:34:48.000Z","uid":104828,"like":1,"dislike":145,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"011d502551111f1b964e845f1d2d98a5cd02df9d","tid":469981,"uid":104828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T00:36:48.000Z","msg":"我同我女朋友一齊就嚟兩年<br />\n事原我同我女朋友近幾個月關係都時好時壞<br />\n上星期因為佢約左人到當日先同我講<br />\n之前叫過好多少叫佢約左人早d同我講<br />\n等我可以早d自己搵下活動<br />\n跟著當然因為咁鬧交啦<br />\n鬧完之後同佢傾<br />\n傾下傾下就話分手 好決絕<br />\n我想挽回番佢<br />\n已經4日<br />\n佢見到我會黑曬面<br />\nwts snapchat成日on但唔會理我<br />\n我去撞佢連手都唔俾拖 唔俾掂<br />\n見佢連手機密碼都改埋<br />\n到底佢依家點諗我<br />\n我仲有冇機會追番佢<br />\n連登嘅各位有經歷過嘅話俾d意見丫<br />\n有機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef8305f94e30bcd721fc1966051e0bbd51bdbc16","tid":469981,"uid":104828,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T00:38:18.000Z","msg":"應該係拖到佢同我一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n定好心放手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc6270357b503ea58a727141c27d98766995cf7","tid":469981,"uid":130151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T00:41:26.000Z","msg":"心淡"},{"pid":"8c186d340d418f451d342435a7ab0fb385d2a4e0","tid":469981,"uid":71096,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T00:44:45.000Z","msg":"條女可能忍左你好耐，算吧~勉強無幸福。"},{"pid":"8a94f24b697eed37b0dbc2b8a539eca3f8224798","tid":469981,"uid":84355,"like":7,"dislike":7,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T00:45:32.000Z","msg":"明明佢錯，做男人做到你好似狗咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0cf7775c2502d048b6216eb18689ae5d85c85e5","tid":469981,"uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T00:47:27.000Z","msg":"佢飛左你"},{"pid":"eb72949f31a2c2376a3521fbdf38d47baa57696a","tid":469981,